Slow Computer Performance

  Problem
User reported that a desktop computer was running very slow during daily tasks.

   Diagnosis
- Checked CPU and RAM usage  
- Identified high startup program load  
- Detected outdated system and drivers  

  Solution
- Disabled unnecessary startup programs  
- Updated Windows and drivers  
- Performed antivirus scan  

  Result
System performance improved significantly and user was able to work without delays.
